=== cmd 0: [addressbook --help] ===
Manage named addresses scoped by chain ID

Usage: treb addressbook [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  set     Set an addressbook entry for the current chain
  remove  Remove an addressbook entry for the current chain
  list    List addressbook entries for the current chain
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --no-color               Disable colored output (also respected via NO_COLOR env var)
  -s, --namespace <NAMESPACE>  Deployment namespace
  -n, --network <NETWORK>      Network name or chain ID
      --non-interactive        Skip interactive prompts (also enabled via TREB_NON_INTERACTIVE=1,
                               CI=true, or non-TTY stdin/stdout)
  -h, --help                   Print help
